export default {
name: 'ShowDataBase',
getArticles: function() {
  this.loading = true;
  this.$http.get(‘/api/article/’)
      .then((response) => {
        this.articles = response.data;
        this.loading = false;
      })
      .catch((err) => {
       this.loading = false;
       console.log(err);
      })
 },
